<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 13:25:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>黄昏海滩远眺</title><link>https://some.pics/69f206cde720f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;傍晚时分，在巴尔海滩眺望大海。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A night time photo, the moon up above in the sky, reflecting in the sea below and illuminating the sky below. A curved lookout point with metal railings is in the bottom of the photo with the horizon off in the distance." height="4012" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/tristy/69f206cde720f.jpg" width="3004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://tristy.some.pics"&gt;@tristy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 13:25:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>牙齿</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1fa197be01</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对不起，我无法处理这个请求。请提供完整的英文内容以便翻译。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A bag of hedgehog food featuring a hedgehog image with big front teeth, highlighting "wholesome nutrition" and benefits like vitamin E, high digestibility, and high protein.' height="6048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/itsbrian/69f1fa197be01.jpg" width="8064"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://itsbrian.some.pics"&gt;@itsbrian&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 12:31:32 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>幻想生物般的栗树新叶</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1f7fa390f2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它看起来几乎像一个奇幻生物，坐在柱子上伸出长长的手臂和手指，也许是想抓住什么、飞走，或者发起攻击……但这不过是栗树正在舒展它的叶子（而我的幻想又在作祟了）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="As mentioned in the description: a b&amp;amp;w picture of a chestnut tree unfurling its leaves. " height="2865" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69f1f7fa390f2.jpg" width="2517"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 12:22:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>鲸鱼Whaley的旅行</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1c375dd22b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Whaley的旅行&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Whaley's trip" height="1263" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/whaley/69f1c375dd22b.png" width="893"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://whaley.some.pics"&gt;@whaley&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 08:38:16 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>早起的鸟儿有虫吃</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1a603647d1</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🏃🏻 早起的鸟儿有虫吃。🙌🏻&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🏃🏻 Iets met vroeg en wormen. 🙌🏻" height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/69f1a603647d1.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 06:32:38 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>